info.senderName: NWS Baltimore/Washington (Washington D.C., Central Maryland, Northern Virginia, Eastern West Virginia)
info.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 19 at 12:58PM EST until January 20 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Baltimore/Washington
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM 8 PM THIS EVENING TO 4 PM EST FRIDAY... * WHAT...West winds 20 to 35 mph with gusts up to 55 mph expected. * WHERE...Portions of western Maryland, western Virginia and eastern West Virginia. * WHEN...From 8 PM this evening to 4 PM EST Friday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
